{"type":"answer","id":2333,"parentType":"question","parentId":533,"uid":167,"contents":"18.4.30更新<br>\n<br>\n&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\n目前不太满意的问题有：<br>\n<br>\n1. 三血和四血没有一种比较合理的区分标准，第一次做的完全随性<br>\n<br>\n2. 董建华和徐嘉诰的技能机制类似，虽然个人认为这个机制都符合这两个人的经历或者特点，但是总还不是坠吼<br>\n<br>\n3. 宋煮鹰的配图我很不满意<br>\n<br>\n&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\n蛤001 长者 茳沢泯<br>\n<br>\n称号考虑过“改变中国”，大家觉得比“长者”吼我会修改。作为三个微小贡献之一的三个代表是必须要体现的，于是有了开局强行钦定的思路。本来相关主公技改为限定技更改代表但是会强度失衡，4血3收益的武将必须要足够吃技术（开局钦定错一个就-2收益）。总体来说我还是挺满意，强度足以作为核心且不无脑。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/4b403d2069196c73a31a6121615088db.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/4b403d2069196c73a31a6121615088db.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/4b403d2069196c73a31a6121615088db.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\n蛤002 没有说要钦定 董先生<br>\n<br>\n按照基本法以及我们的决定权董先生一定要连任。一技能是因为在职期间很多人反对他仍然位置坐的好好的，二技能意为无人反对就连任。一个防御能力很不错还不能不动的盾将，强度尚可。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/62b9e5b254800d286f920bd192561ec5.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/62b9e5b254800d286f920bd192561ec5.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/62b9e5b254800d286f920bd192561ec5.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\n蛤003 谈笑风生 华莱士<br>\n<br>\n我个人最满意的一个设计，表面谈笑风生实则绵里藏针。可以跟队友刷牌也可以输出但是很吃技术，算计不好会伤到自己人/自己受伤。定位是很脆的刷牌核。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/3d2d28a53b267305d6b63a7b9ad72b2c.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/3d2d28a53b267305d6b63a7b9ad72b2c.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/3d2d28a53b267305d6b63a7b9ad72b2c.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\n蛤004 洋文好的很 郭伟华<br>\n<br>\n刷牌体系中能够把牌存起来的一个角色，越拖二院越厉害。二技能其实没多强，要拿别人牌不容易的。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/756cc3910e6f52b744ed467dd0913a8e.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/756cc3910e6f52b744ed467dd0913a8e.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/756cc3910e6f52b744ed467dd0913a8e.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n蛤005 气象学家 徐嘉诰<br>\n<br>\n没有收益但是可以显著提高防御能力及手牌质量的角色，别人是不知道你选了谁的，所以有些套路可以玩。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/85ec84465c4f2ce22e2b30bc8a1148c4.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/85ec84465c4f2ce22e2b30bc8a1148c4.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/85ec84465c4f2ce22e2b30bc8a1148c4.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n蛤006 naive的宝华姐<br>\n<br>\n用牌系武将，总归也要有个跑得比谁都要快的输出。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/2dab8863e240fd5930ca5f794e1ca91f.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/2dab8863e240fd5930ca5f794e1ca91f.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/2dab8863e240fd5930ca5f794e1ca91f.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n蛤007 粉饰太平宋祖英<br>\n<br>\n没什么好说的。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/b8de97c9ab0efe6bc1d6c87c74a8f72b.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/b8de97c9ab0efe6bc1d6c87c74a8f72b.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/b8de97c9ab0efe6bc1d6c87c74a8f72b.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n暂时就写了这7个，之后不定期更新<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/4b403d2069196c73a31a6121615088db.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/4b403d2069196c73a31a6121615088db.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/4b403d2069196c73a31a6121615088db.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/62b9e5b254800d286f920bd192561ec5.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/62b9e5b254800d286f920bd192561ec5.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/62b9e5b254800d286f920bd192561ec5.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/3d2d28a53b267305d6b63a7b9ad72b2c.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/3d2d28a53b267305d6b63a7b9ad72b2c.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/3d2d28a53b267305d6b63a7b9ad72b2c.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/756cc3910e6f52b744ed467dd0913a8e.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/756cc3910e6f52b744ed467dd0913a8e.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/756cc3910e6f52b744ed467dd0913a8e.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/85ec84465c4f2ce22e2b30bc8a1148c4.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/85ec84465c4f2ce22e2b30bc8a1148c4.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/85ec84465c4f2ce22e2b30bc8a1148c4.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/2dab8863e240fd5930ca5f794e1ca91f.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/2dab8863e240fd5930ca5f794e1ca91f.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/2dab8863e240fd5930ca5f794e1ca91f.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/b8de97c9ab0efe6bc1d6c87c74a8f72b.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/b8de97c9ab0efe6bc1d6c87c74a8f72b.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180430/b8de97c9ab0efe6bc1d6c87c74a8f72b.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2018-04-30","agreeCount":11,"discussionCount":0}